ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENT

When citing or implementing SNOMI, attribution must include:

  SNOMI — Standard Nomenclature of Influence Metrics (v[version])
  https://github.com/rayanebenabs/SNOMI

Short form for reports and documents:
  "Metrics cited per SNOMI v2.1 (snomi.io)"

